name: FrameData
0:
”Alexa open Frame Data”
”Alexa ask Frame Data how many frames is Chun-Li's standing heavy punch on block”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: frame data
des: This Frame Data voice app is a tool to help new and experience Street Fighter V players learn the frame data from all 40 characters in the game. This app serves as a quicker way to fetch this frame data opposed to having to look it up online every time. This can also be used during your match to help you quickly adapt your strategy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
